import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import ChefAllRestaurants from '../Body/ChefOfTheWeek/ChefAllRestaurants'
import AllRestaurants from '../Body/PopularRestaurants/AllRestaurants'
import AllDishes from '../Body/SignaturesCarousel/AllDishes'
import Footer from '../Footer/Footer'
import Header from '../Header/Header'
import HomePageEmptyBag from '../HomePage/HomePageEmptyBag'
import MobileHomePage from '../HomePage/MobileHomePage'

export default function Layout() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
        <Header/>
        <Routes>
            <Route path='' element={<MobileHomePage/>}/>
            <Route path='/AllRestaurants' element={<AllRestaurants/>}/>
            <Route path='/ChefAllRestaurants' element={<ChefAllRestaurants/>}/>
            <Route path='/AllDishes' element={<AllDishes/>}/>
            <Route path='/HomePageEmptyBag' element={<HomePageEmptyBag/>}/>
        </Routes>
        <Footer/>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
